47
00:55:58,855 --> 00:56:01,756
lt will take me a month to make the sword.

48
00:56:04,027 --> 00:56:07,895
l suggest you spend it practicing.

49
00:57:37,921 --> 00:57:39,582
l've completed doing...

50
00:57:41,691 --> 00:57:46,219
