163
02:33:13,017 --> 02:33:13,574
Yes.

164
02:33:14,552 --> 02:33:15,610
ls it your wish to die?

165
02:33:16,187 --> 02:33:16,778
No.

166
02:33:18,756 --> 02:33:19,688
